Hi ha indicadors de carretera. &Eacute;s accessible per al p&uacute;blic en general.','Se accede desde la carretera Me-12 de Mah&oacute;n a San Climent. Entre el punto kilom&eacute;trico 3 y 4, a la derecha, se entra en el camino rural de Torell&oacute; Vell y a 600 metros est&aacute; el yacimiento.<br />
Hay indicadores de carretera.','<p dir="ltr">Access is along the Me-12 road from Ma&oacute; to Sant Climent. Between kilometres 3 and 4 is a turnoff to the right onto the Torell&oacute; Vell country road. Follow this road 600 m to the site. Road signs are posted.</p>
